<%= stylesheet_link_tag "back-partners-show-edit", :media => "all"  %>   
<% @title = "CGT Partners Page Back - Edit Partners Show Column" -%>
<% @header = "CGT Partners Page Back - Edit Partners Show Column" -%>
<div id="block-mgt">  
  <%= render(:partial => 'menu') %>     
  <div id="operate-mgt">
    <div id="operate-intro">
      <h3>Information About Editing Partners Show Column</h3>
      <p>In the column, we need partner's four information - logo, name, brief and its URL. Logo picture size is 80X60px, brief box size is 280X60px (190 letters), and font is 10px, its URL is just a link on the logo.
      <p>After you input the new content, then it will replace your old one that will be changed. 
      <p>When you are sure that you need to input the new content, please edit your information below.
      </p>
    </div><!-- end #operate-intro -->

    <div id="operate-area">
      <h3>Edit Partners Show Column</h3>
      
      <div id="operate-new">
        <% form_for :partner,@partner,:url => { :action => "update",:id => @partner.id }, :html => { :method => :post , :multipart => true } do |f| %>

          <div class="word">
            <p align="center">Update Partner's Name:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(Less than 40 letters.)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <%= f.text_field :pa_name ,:maxlength=>40,:size=>50 %>
          </div>
          <div class="word">
            <p>Update Partner's Brief:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(Only Text Available. Less than 190 letters.)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="message">
            <%= f.text_area :pa_desc,:cols=>70,:rows=>11 %>
          </div>
          <div class="word">
            <p align="center">Update Partner's Logo Image File Name:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(Less than 40 letters.)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <%= f.file_field :uploaded_data,:maxlength=>40,:size=>50  %>
          </div>
          <div class="word">
            <p align="center">Update Partner's URL:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(Less than 40 letters.)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <%= f.text_field :pa_url,:maxlength=>40,:size=>50  %>
          </div>
          <div class="word">
            <p align="center">Update Author:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(Less than 40 letters.)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <%= f.text_field :pa_author,:maxlength=>40,:size=>50  %>
          </div>
          <div class="word">
            <p align="center">Update Admin:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(Less than 40 letters.)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <input name="admin" type="text" class="input" value="Original Admin is displayed here" maxlength=40 size=50 />
          </div>
          <div class="div">
            <p>
              <%= f.submit "Edit Content" ,:onclick => "New Content Has Been Successfully Input!" %>
            </p>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>    <!-- End #operate-new -->


      <div id="operate-buttons">
        <ul>
          <li><%= link_to "Back" ,:action => "list"%></li>
        </ul>
      </div>  <!-- End #operate-bottons -->

    </div>   <!-- end #operate-area -->
  </div> <!-- end #operate-mgt -->
</div> <!-- end #block-mgt --> 